Package com.hyperwallet.android.model.graphql.error

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Extension
    The Extension class represents Hyperwallet specific data related to error conditions for GraphQL.
    GqlError
    The GqlError class represents a GraphQL error as defined by the June 2018 specification.
    GqlErrors
    The GqlErrors class is a container for the list of GqlErrors.
    Location
    The Location class represents the index location in the serialized JSON structure of the associated GqlError.
